metadata.name: Filband
metadata.description:
Artist: Amir Shirazian

This photo was taken in the North of Iran a place called Filband. The combination of high mountains and dense forests which pass through a large number of white clouds has turned the village special. 
Finding and waiting for sunset and the time which sun going to cover by cloud gave me this sunbeam.
This photo is created by stitching  3 photos to get this wide-angle view with high resolution. 

size:
8220*3158

1/1
